                        </LONG-NAME>
                        <DESC>
                          <L-2 L="EN">This function is used to read out a given number of ARP table entries per EthIfCtrl. If given number is bigger then available ARP table entries in use, the function only returns the number of used ARP table entries.</L-2>
                        </DESC>
